==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Toothsome
<hw>Tooth"some</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Grateful to the
taste; palatable.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Tooth"some*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Tooth"some*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Though less <qex>toothsome</qex> to me, they were more wholesome
for me.</q> <rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Toothwort</ent>⟦br⟧
